{"type": "user_message", "content": "<task-notification>\n<task-id>a9b299c1543a2540d</task-id>\n<tool-use-id>toolu_01QCb1Fdky8UjygmZFNQwdN8</tool-use-id>\n<status>completed</status>\n<summary>Agent \"Extract DNA from smaller books\" completed</summary>\n<result>The extraction is complete. Here is a detailed summary of what was produced.\n\n---\n\n## Extraction Complete: 63 New DNA Elements\n\n**Output file:** `C:\\Users\\ISMAEL_MELLO\\Downloads\\mega-brain-premium\\artifacts\\insights\\russell-brunson\\pdf-extracts\\EXTRACTION-Network-Cookbook.md`\n\n### Element Counts by Layer and Book\n\n| Layer | Network Marketing Secrets | Funnel Hacker's Cookbook | Total |\n|-------|--------------------------|------------------------|-------|\n| L1 PHILOSOPHIES (PHI) | 8 | 5 | **13** |\n| L2 MENTAL_MODELS (MM) | 6 | 5 | **11** |\n| L3 HEURISTICS (HEUR) | 7 | 8 | **15** |\n| L4 FRAMEWORKS (FW) | 5 | 12 | **17** |\n| L5 METHODOLOGIES (MET) | 4 | 3 | **7** |\n| **TOTAL** | **30** | **33** | **63** |\n\n### Key NEW Domains (Not Present in Existing 271 Elements)\n\n1. **Network Marketing / MLM mechanics** -- The entire domain of duplication, downline building, and the four phases network marketers go through (NFL Club, Anti-Sales Department, Clone Wars, Homeless Man with Ferrari) is brand new content.\n\n2. **Three Lost Funnels** -- Bridge Funnel (mimics three-way calls), Home Party Funnel (mimics live product demos), and Hotel Meeting Funnel (mimics weekly hotel presentations) are specific to network marketing and not covered in video transcriptions.\n\n3. **Viral Loop** -- The four-step selling sequence (Epiphany Bridge, Demo, Call to Action, Duplication) that must occur in each funnel for referral-based businesses.\n\n4. **22 Funnel Recipe Taxonomy** -- A comprehensive catalog of all funnel types organized into Lead (7), Buyer (5), Event (4), and Other (6) funnels, each with specific page counts and build times.\n\n5. **Page-Level Recipes** -- 30+ individual page recipes with specific ingredients, including Presale Pages (4), Optin Pages (4), Thank You Pages (", "metadata": {"session_id": "b7473510-77ef-4c04-9110-cf2b7c914c57", "transcript_path": "C:\\Users\\ISMAEL_MELLO\\.claude\\projects\\C--Users-ISMAEL-MELLO-Downloads-mega-brain-premium\\b7473510-77ef-4c04-9110-cf2b7c914c57.jsonl", "cwd": "C:\\Users\\ISMAEL_MELLO\\Downloads\\mega-brain-premium", "permission_mode": "default", "hook_event_name": "UserPromptSubmit", "prompt": "<task-notification>\n<task-id>a9b299c1543a2540d</task-id>\n<tool-use-id>toolu_01QCb1Fdky8UjygmZFNQwdN8</tool-use-id>\n<status>completed</status>\n<summary>Agent \"Extract DNA from smaller books\" completed</summary>\n<result>The extraction is complete. Here is a detailed summary of what was produced.\n\n---\n\n## Extraction Complete: 63 New DNA Elements\n\n**Output file:** `C:\\Users\\ISMAEL_MELLO\\Downloads\\mega-brain-premium\\artifacts\\insights\\russell-brunson\\pdf-extracts\\EXTRACTION-Network-Cookbook.md`\n\n### Element Counts by Layer and Book\n\n| Layer | Network Marketing Secrets | Funnel Hacker's Cookbook | Total |\n|-------|--------------------------|------------------------|-------|\n| L1 PHILOSOPHIES (PHI) | 8 | 5 | **13** |\n| L2 MENTAL_MODELS (MM) | 6 | 5 | **11** |\n| L3 HEURISTICS (HEUR) | 7 | 8 | **15** |\n| L4 FRAMEWORKS (FW) | 5 | 12 | **17** |\n| L5 METHODOLOGIES (MET) | 4 | 3 | **7** |\n| **TOTAL** | **30** | **33** | **63** |\n\n### Key NEW Domains (Not Present in Existing 271 Elements)\n\n1. **Network Marketing / MLM mechanics** -- The entire domain of duplication, downline building, and the four phases network marketers go through (NFL Club, Anti-Sales Department, Clone Wars, Homeless Man with Ferrari) is brand new content.\n\n2. **Three Lost Funnels** -- Bridge Funnel (mimics three-way calls), Home Party Funnel (mimics live product demos), and Hotel Meeting Funnel (mimics weekly hotel presentations) are specific to network marketing and not covered in video transcriptions.\n\n3. **Viral Loop** -- The four-step selling sequence (Epiphany Bridge, Demo, Call to Action, Duplication) that must occur in each funnel for referral-based businesses.\n\n4. **22 Funnel Recipe Taxonomy** -- A comprehensive catalog of all funnel types organized into Lead (7), Buyer (5), Event (4), and Other (6) funnels, each with specific page counts and build times.\n\n5. **Page-Level Recipes** -- 30+ individual page recipes with specific ingredients, including Presale Pages (4), Optin Pages (4), Thank You Pages (4), Sales Pages (3), Order Forms (5), OTO Pages (2), Webinar Pages (4), Membership Pages (2), and Affiliate Pages (2).\n\n### Key Numerical Benchmarks Captured\n\n- Webinar replay pages convert highest when pulled down after **48 to 72 hours**\n- Home Party Funnel generated **1.5 million leads in 6 weeks**\n- Bridge Funnel Page 1 setup takes **3 minutes** (1 minute with template)\n- YouTube Live supports **up to 9 people** in hangout\n- Sign into YouTube Live **1 hour before** event, get participants in **15 minutes before** start\n- Funnel build times range from **15 minutes** (Survey Funnel) to **2 hours** (Summit/Product Launch)\n\n### Key Conversion Insights\n\n- Curiosity-based headlines produce the highest squeeze page conversion rates\n- Reverse squeeze pages convert lower but produce higher quality leads\n- Click pops (popups) dramatically increase conversion vs embedded forms\n- Same-page order forms on VSL pages dramatically increase conversion\n- Long-form sales letters often convert better than video in current environment\n- Inserting a bridge page into a non-converting funnel often increases sales page conversion\n- 2-Step order form abandonment recovery (follow up on incomplete Step 2) dramatically increases conversion\n\nThe document also includes a **Page Recipe Reference** quick-lookup table, a **Funnel Build Time Reference** table, and a **Cross-Reference** section mapping which elements are entirely new domains versus deepening existing coverage from the 271 video transcription elements.</result>\n<usage><total_tokens>166830</total_tokens><tool_uses>12</tool_uses><duration_ms>288004</duration_ms></usage>\n</task-notification>\nFull transcript available at: C:\\Users\\ISMAEL~1\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\claude\\C--Users-ISMAEL-MELLO-Downloads-mega-brain-premium\\tasks\\a9b299c1543a2540d.output"}, "_timestamp": "2026-03-01T17:28:26.542406", "_id": "4103c646"}
